'''Cartann''' was the large country on [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]], controlling over half of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] landmass. Its [[Perator]] was [[Pekaelic ke Teldan]] until [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]], when his eldest son [[Balass ke Teldan]] took the throne. It also possessed a large air force consisting mainly of modern [[Blade-32 superiority fighter]]s. Its capital was [[Cartann City]]. It was overthrown by the [[Yedagon Confederacy]].

==History==
In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] and [[Ben Skywalker]] visited the [[Dammant Killers]] [[Missile/Legends|missile]] factory in Cartann, where they discovered that the company was overproducing so as to sell large amounts of missiles to parties outside the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]].

